Class IngredientTblImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • kaitech.api.database.AbstractTable
      • kaitech.database.IngredientTblImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IngredientTable
    public class IngredientTblImpl
extends AbstractTable
implements IngredientTable
    IngredientTblImpl extends AbstractTable, implements the IngredientTable interface, and permits limited access to the data stored in the ingredients table.
